{"id": "ChIJ2zkYN5t_hYARL-JFN8A5-p8", "rating": 4.5, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 1069, "displayName": {"text": "Marugame Udon", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJ2zkYN5t_hYARL-JFN8A5-p8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xCaFdERllNVGxKWnpCdk1URnNhVloyVW1STGFVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Great experience at Marugame Udon! The udon was fresh and chewy, the broth was flavorful, and the tempura topping was crispy and delicious. The drink was refreshing as well. Service was fast and friendly, and the restaurant had a clean, comfortable atmosphere. I would definitely come back again.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Great experience at Marugame Udon! The udon was fresh and chewy, the broth was flavorful, and the tempura topping was crispy and delicious. The drink was refreshing as well. Service was fast and friendly, and the restaurant had a clean, comfortable atmosphere. I would definitely come back again.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Chenfei Peng", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112490236512691894116/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLtv4GbrOf3vqNxUp9-oRsEz6t7nlhnJMGJheI4Hs1F_nxhPQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-25T20:00:33.094701093Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xCaFdERllNVGxKWnpCdk1URnNhVloyVW1STGFVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xCaFdERllNVGxKWnpCdk1URnNhVloyVW1STGFVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f9b371839db:0x9ffa39c03745e22f"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ2zkYN5t_hYARL-JFN8A5-p8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT214UFFuUTRYMVY2TkUxMU9YQmtOVXQwWTI5clFVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "It is a great spot for comforting and authentic Japanese food. The udon noodles were freshly made, thick, and perfectly chewy, and the broth was light yet very flavorful. I appreciated being able to customize the bowl with different toppings, which made the experience fun and satisfying. The service was fast and well organized, even when there was a line, and the prices were reasonable for the quality and portion size. A solid choice for a quick, delicious meal if you’re craving udon in Berkeley.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "It is a great spot for comforting and authentic Japanese food. The udon noodles were freshly made, thick, and perfectly chewy, and the broth was light yet very flavorful. I appreciated being able to customize the bowl with different toppings, which made the experience fun and satisfying. The service was fast and well organized, even when there was a line, and the prices were reasonable for the quality and portion size. A solid choice for a quick, delicious meal if you’re craving udon in Berkeley.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Windy Oktanaura", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107413482159125787768/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcDVeKCMRhzICfnTqoedl8KokC18mVuED8B7Inu1oTYWFv2zz-=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-07T08:01:18.960260542Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT214UFFuUTRYMVY2TkUxMU9YQmtOVXQwWTI5clFVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT214UFFuUTRYMVY2TkUxMU9YQmtOVXQwWTI5clFVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f9b371839db:0x9ffa39c03745e22f"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ2zkYN5t_hYARL-JFN8A5-p8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2taWGVXOXpiRk5XY1ZWTGFEY3RkV2g1WjNKS1VFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "8/10 (this location) | 9/10 overall\n\nHow can you go wrong with Marugame Udon? Seriously. It’s one of those spots that just hits every time. This location gets an 8/10 from me—still solid, still satisfying—but overall, the brand is easily a 9/10 because it’s just sooooo good.\n\nIf you’re going for the first time (or even if you’re not), do yourself a favor and get the beef or nikutama. The broth is rich, savory, and comforting, and the noodles have that perfect chewy texture that makes every bite worth it. It’s simple food done really well.\n\nAnd don’t skimp on the tempura. That’s where people mess up. Load up your tray—shrimp, sweet potato, whatever catches your eye. It’s crispy, fresh, and honestly half the experience.\n\nQuick, casual, and consistently delicious. Hard to miss here.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "8/10 (this location) | 9/10 overall\n\nHow can you go wrong with Marugame Udon? Seriously. It’s one of those spots that just hits every time. This location gets an 8/10 from me—still solid, still satisfying—but overall, the brand is easily a 9/10 because it’s just sooooo good.\n\nIf you’re going for the first time (or even if you’re not), do yourself a favor and get the beef or nikutama. The broth is rich, savory, and comforting, and the noodles have that perfect chewy texture that makes every bite worth it. It’s simple food done really well.\n\nAnd don’t skimp on the tempura. That’s where people mess up. Load up your tray—shrimp, sweet potato, whatever catches your eye. It’s crispy, fresh, and honestly half the experience.\n\nQuick, casual, and consistently delicious. Hard to miss here.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Nathan Tran", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105423701810297160534/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0YwO9dxP6Tmj-jIVMQo88dC1LZI7kmC6TzRrLxg0S5fbwBNC-=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-17T11:28:33.993212618Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2taWGVXOXpiRk5XY1ZWTGFEY3RkV2g1WjNKS1VFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2taWGVXOXpiRk5XY1ZWTGFEY3RkV2g1WjNKS1VFRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f9b371839db:0x9ffa39c03745e22f"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ2zkYN5t_hYARL-JFN8A5-p8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwS1kxOTZja1JCYTJzeGNYaFNSSFpmUW1SVVpVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "My son attends UC Berkeley, so I come to Berkeley at the beginning of each semester. This time, he took me to Marugame Udon, and it was such a great experience. The food was simple, fresh, and delicious, and I loved the whole concept. There’s nothing like this where I live — definitely one of the best!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "My son attends UC Berkeley, so I come to Berkeley at the beginning of each semester. This time, he took me to Marugame Udon, and it was such a great experience. The food was simple, fresh, and delicious, and I loved the whole concept. There’s nothing like this where I live — definitely one of the best!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "sanghee joo", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112459477546180883373/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK3eHsUdy0BpgcZZOgdGzBtq-__VANtv4e9e_dA-2EzsyotxA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-02T07:15:16.985887482Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwS1kxOTZja1JCYTJzeGNYaFNSSFpmUW1SVVpVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xwS1kxOTZja1JCYTJzeGNYaFNSSFpmUW1SVVpVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f9b371839db:0x9ffa39c03745e22f"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ2zkYN5t_hYARL-JFN8A5-p8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21oQlRrdGxUV1ZqUkZGbFpFcHJOR1J4Vm1ZMVJIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Now that I’m done with UC Berkeley, I can confidently claim that this has always been a very tasty ramen restaurant. I would go here whenever I had in-person campus visits. The thick vegan noodles with carrots, broth, and cabbage are very delicious.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Now that I’m done with UC Berkeley, I can confidently claim that this has always been a very tasty ramen restaurant. I would go here whenever I had in-person campus visits. The thick vegan noodles with carrots, broth, and cabbage are very delicious.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Angelina Cayabyab", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107186419237091179136/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVrKi_fV1atb_JdDiLG4-A_oB2m_NCVuBTNLf5MSZU9vz7svEM=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-27T00:56:44.710348506Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21oQlRrdGxUV1ZqUkZGbFpFcHJOR1J4Vm1ZMVJIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21oQlRrdGxUV1ZqUkZGbFpFcHJOR1J4Vm1ZMVJIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857f9b371839db:0x9ffa39c03745e22f"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJ2zkYN5t_hYARL-JFN8A5-p8/photos/AWCwydiTRKFy_GAlpu4YG7KxSdnQDdStnAxhqcAaSgt6grvUHit45kgRJfPyw0l4b-WSViPsbVDrfdhyPlbHpgZauvt2k6g7kOwctz0G7ZVQjkJfct_mlK6aCCkbVujJVYcWBXiP_T5Cx4-xIC6wnMdPGrds0-n8ywcpE27CNPlSST8ZUEWIC3mndZXkFzWsjgUSKDso2HOe_OXs6kbEirUtcq9JzZ7RqTXjx1L1yd9fw4nh4Fg1dH5jA27jX6M8nr7jskS1Mlb6LA_rtfH3F8VjzpafiSNLdizivC7hmTOiC3JATdoZ7Epjuj2S6_Km0KJPEpfNtjQGNe3ncqNcptxuwXiAT6eKo4XZyw9s5fROBpnWtSkB_yAS4k8DtGXA0Js_3fGdB3PNfKNAOr1IbJk0IvCl2VDO1TpQ3_FDkqMwTSE_5A", "widthPx": 4032, "heightPx": 3024, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Pim Kang", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/104025786518461894821", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUIwhzLUwXgQmIMQxEweJhREls14